info.description: Test model for PID controller with optional reverse action

equation: pulse.offset + (if time < pulse.startTime or pulse.nperiod == 0 or pulse.nperiod > 0 and pulse.count >= pulse.nperiod then 0.0 else if time < pulse.T_start + pulse.T_width then pulse.amplitude else 0.0)
if limPID.D.zeroGain then 0.0 else DIVISION(limPID.D.u - limPID.D.x, limPID.D.T)
if limPID.D.zeroGain then 0.0 else limPID.D.k * DIVISION(limPID.D.u - limPID.D.x, limPID.D.T)
limPID.addPID.k1 * limPID.P.y + limPID.addPID.k2 * limPID.D.y + limPID.addPID.k3 * limPID.I.y

homotopy(smooth(0, if noEvent(limPID.addSat.u2 > limPID.limiter.uMax) then limPID.limiter.uMax else if noEvent(limPID.addSat.u2 < limPID.limiter.uMin) then limPID.limiter.uMin else limPID.addSat.u2), limPID.addSat.u2)
limPID.addI.k1 * limPID.u_s + limPID.addI.k2 * const.k + limPID.addI.k3 * limPID.addI.u3
if limPIDRev.D.zeroGain then 0.0 else DIVISION(limPIDRev.D.u - limPIDRev.D.x, limPIDRev.D.T)
if limPIDRev.D.zeroGain then 0.0 else limPIDRev.D.k * DIVISION(limPIDRev.D.u - limPIDRev.D.x, limPIDRev.D.T)
limPIDRev.addPID.k1 * limPIDRev.P.y + limPIDRev.addPID.k2 * limPIDRev.D.y + limPIDRev.addPID.k3 * limPIDRev.I.y

homotopy(smooth(0, if noEvent(limPIDRev.addSat.u2 > limPIDRev.limiter.uMax) then limPIDRev.limiter.uMax else if noEvent(limPIDRev.addSat.u2 < limPIDRev.limiter.uMin) then limPIDRev.limiter.uMin else limPIDRev.addSat.u2), limPIDRev.addSat.u2)
limPIDRev.addI.k1 * limPID.u_s + limPIDRev.addI.k2 * const.k + limPIDRev.addI.k3 * limPIDRev.addI.u3
if limPIDOri.D.zeroGain then 0.0 else DIVISION(limPIDOri.D.u - limPIDOri.D.x, limPIDOri.D.T)
if limPIDOri.D.zeroGain then 0.0 else limPIDOri.D.k * DIVISION(limPIDOri.D.u - limPIDOri.D.x, limPIDOri.D.T)
limPIDOri.addPID.k1 * limPIDOri.P.y + limPIDOri.addPID.k2 * limPIDOri.D.y + limPIDOri.addPID.k3 * limPIDOri.I.y

homotopy(smooth(0, if limPIDOri.addSat.u2 > limPIDOri.limiter.uMax then limPIDOri.limiter.uMax else if limPIDOri.addSat.u2 < limPIDOri.limiter.uMin then limPIDOri.limiter.uMin else limPIDOri.addSat.u2), limPIDOri.addSat.u2)
limPIDOri.addI.k1 * limPID.u_s + limPIDOri.addI.k2 * const.k + limPIDOri.addI.k3 * limPIDOri.addI.u3

assert(limPIDOri.limiter.uMax >= limPIDOri.limiter.uMin, "Limiter: Limits must be consistent. However, uMax (=" + String(limPIDOri.limiter.uMax, 0, true, 6) + ") < uMin (=" + String(limPIDOri.limiter.uMin, 0, true, 6) + ")");
assert(limPIDRev.yMax >= limPIDRev.yMin, "LimPID: Limits must be consistent. However, yMax (=" + String(limPIDRev.yMax, 0, true, 6) + ") < yMin (=" + String(limPIDRev.yMin, 0, true, 6) + ")");

assert(limPIDRev.limiter.uMax >= limPIDRev.limiter.uMin, "Limiter: Limits must be consistent. However, uMax (=" + String(limPIDRev.limiter.uMax, 0, true, 6) + ") < uMin (=" + String(limPIDRev.limiter.uMin, 0, true, 6) + ")");
assert(limPID.yMax >= limPID.yMin, "LimPID: Limits must be consistent. However, yMax (=" + String(limPID.yMax, 0, true, 6) + ") < yMin (=" + String(limPID.yMin, 0, true, 6) + ")");

assert(limPID.limiter.uMax >= limPID.limiter.uMin, "Limiter: Limits must be consistent. However, uMax (=" + String(limPID.limiter.uMax, 0, true, 6) + ") < uMin (=" + String(limPID.limiter.uMin, 0, true, 6) + ")");

pulse.offset + (if time < pulse.startTime or pulse.nperiod == 0 or pulse.nperiod > 0 and pulse.count >= pulse.nperiod then 0.0 else if time < pulse.T_start + pulse.T_width then pulse.amplitude else 0.0)
if limPID.D.zeroGain then 0.0 else DIVISION(limPID.D.u - limPID.D.x, limPID.D.T)

limPID.addPID.k1 * limPID.P.y + limPID.addPID.k2 * limPID.D.y + limPID.addPID.k3 * limPID.I.y
limPID.addI.k1 * limPID.u_s + limPID.addI.k2 * const.k + limPID.addI.k3 * limPID.addI.u3

limPIDRev.addI.k1 * limPID.u_s + limPIDRev.addI.k2 * const.k + limPIDRev.addI.k3 * limPIDRev.addI.u3

limPIDOri.addPID.k1 * limPIDOri.P.y + limPIDOri.addPID.k2 * limPIDOri.D.y + limPIDOri.addPID.k3 * limPIDOri.I.y
limPIDOri.addI.k1 * limPID.u_s + limPIDOri.addI.k2 * const.k + limPIDOri.addI.k3 * limPIDOri.addI.u3

pulse.offset + (if time < pulse.startTime or pulse.nperiod == 0 or pulse.nperiod > 0 and pulse.count >= pulse.nperiod then 0.0 else if time < pulse.T_start + pulse.T_width then pulse.amplitude else 0.0)
if limPIDOri.D.zeroGain then 0.0 else limPIDOri.D.k * DIVISION(limPIDOri.D.u - limPIDOri.D.x, limPIDOri.D.T)
if limPIDOri.D.zeroGain then 0.0 else DIVISION(limPIDOri.D.u - limPIDOri.D.x, limPIDOri.D.T)
limPIDOri.addPID.k1 * limPIDOri.P.y + limPIDOri.addPID.k2 * limPIDOri.D.y + limPIDOri.addPID.k3 * limPIDOri.I.y
smooth(0, if limPIDOri.addSat.u2 > limPIDOri.limiter.uMax then limPIDOri.limiter.uMax else if limPIDOri.addSat.u2 < limPIDOri.limiter.uMin then limPIDOri.limiter.uMin else limPIDOri.addSat.u2)

if limPIDRev.D.zeroGain then 0.0 else DIVISION(limPIDRev.D.u - limPIDRev.D.x, limPIDRev.D.T)
limPIDRev.addPID.k1 * limPIDRev.P.y + limPIDRev.addPID.k2 * limPIDRev.D.y + limPIDRev.addPID.k3 * limPIDRev.I.y

smooth(0, if noEvent(limPIDRev.addSat.u2 > limPIDRev.limiter.uMax) then limPIDRev.limiter.uMax else if noEvent(limPIDRev.addSat.u2 < limPIDRev.limiter.uMin) then limPIDRev.limiter.uMin else limPIDRev.addSat.u2)
limPIDRev.addI.k1 * limPID.u_s + limPIDRev.addI.k2 * const.k + limPIDRev.addI.k3 * limPIDRev.addI.u3
if limPID.D.zeroGain then 0.0 else limPID.D.k * DIVISION(limPID.D.u - limPID.D.x, limPID.D.T)
if limPID.D.zeroGain then 0.0 else DIVISION(limPID.D.u - limPID.D.x, limPID.D.T)
limPID.addPID.k1 * limPID.P.y + limPID.addPID.k2 * limPID.D.y + limPID.addPID.k3 * limPID.I.y
smooth(0, if noEvent(limPID.addSat.u2 > limPID.limiter.uMax) then limPID.limiter.uMax else if noEvent(limPID.addSat.u2 < limPID.limiter.uMin) then limPID.limiter.uMin else limPID.addSat.u2)
limPID.addI.k1 * limPID.u_s + limPID.addI.k2 * const.k + limPID.addI.k3 * limPID.addI.u3

assert(if noEvent(time > assertEquality1.t0) then noEvent(abs(assertEquality1.u1 - assertEquality.u1) < assertEquality1.threShold) else true, assertEquality1.message + "
" + "  time       = " + String(time, 0, true, 6) + "
" + "  u1         = " + String(assertEquality1.u1, 0, true, 6) + "
" + "  u2         = " + String(assertEquality.u1, 0, true, 6) + "
" + "  abs(u1-u2) = " + String(abs(assertEquality1.u1 - assertEquality.u1), 0, true, 6) + "
" + "  threShold  = " + String(assertEquality1.threShold, 0, true, 6));

assert(if noEvent(time > assertEquality.t0) then noEvent(abs(assertEquality.u1 - assertEquality.u2) < assertEquality.threShold) else true, assertEquality.message + "
" + "  time       = " + String(time, 0, true, 6) + "
" + "  u1         = " + String(assertEquality.u1, 0, true, 6) + "
" + "  u2         = " + String(assertEquality.u2, 0, true, 6) + "
" + "  abs(u1-u2) = " + String(abs(assertEquality.u1 - assertEquality.u2), 0, true, 6) + "
" + "  threShold  = " + String(assertEquality.threShold, 0, true, 6));

assert(limPIDOri.limiter.uMax >= limPIDOri.limiter.uMin, "Limiter: Limits must be consistent. However, uMax (=" + String(limPIDOri.limiter.uMax, 0, true, 6) + ") < uMin (=" + String(limPIDOri.limiter.uMin, 0, true, 6) + ")");

assert(pulse.width >= 1e-60 and pulse.width <= 100.0, "Variable violating min/max constraint: 1e-60 <= pulse.width <= 100.0, has value: " + String(pulse.width, "g"));
assert(pulse.period >= 1e-60, "Variable violating min constraint: 1e-60 <= pulse.period, has value: " + String(pulse.period, "g"));

assert(limPID.controllerType >= Modelica.Blocks.Types.SimpleController.P and limPID.controllerType <= Modelica.Blocks.Types.SimpleController.PID, "Variable violating min/max constraint: Modelica.Blocks.Types.SimpleController.P <= limPID.controllerType <= Modelica.Blocks.Types.SimpleController.PID, has value: " + String(limPID.controllerType, "d"));
